</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Timeline: How Trump And WHO Reacted At Key Moments During The Coronavirus Crisis : Goats and Soda</b>   <b data-is-speakable>How did the president respond to key moments during the pandemic? And how did representatives of the World Health Organization respond during the same period?</b>
